Rockhopper to Drill at Least 3 More Wells at Sea Lion, FT Says

-- B y   N a n d i n i   S u k u m a r
-- 
2011-04-23T13:55:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-23/rockhopper-to-drill-at-least-3-more-wells-at-sea-lion-ft-says.html
Rockhopper Exploration Plc , the
only oil explorer to make a potentially commercial discovery in
the Falkland Islands, plans to drill at least three more
appraisal wells at its Sea Lion discovery this year, the
Financial Times reported, citing an interview with Chief
Executive Officer Sam Moody.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
 arummer@bloomberg.net  